Solicit is disorganized. Solicit is a chance to say, "I think it would be good to do this." 

Solicit looks for the formal details that are required in Document, but it does not require them.

Solicit should just have a field for idea.


author
idea
why

This matches the format of the Agile user stories. As a <role> I want to <idea> so that <why>.
